07:34.329 --> 07:37.366
William was a kind man
and a great father.

07:37.582 --> 07:39.288
He was involved in the community.

07:39.501 --> 07:42.334
-When our daughter was in school--
-How many kids do you have?

07:42.545 --> 07:44.376
