11:09.711 --> 11:13.124
-You must be Mr. Harris.
-Yes.

11:13.298 --> 11:15.914
Where's your son?
I was told the appointment is for him.

11:16.134 --> 11:19.968
Oh, it should be, but, you know,
my wife doesn't really believe in therapy.

11:20.180 --> 11:23.263
You know, she thinks people like you
do more harm than good.

11:23.766 --> 11:25.973
Do you, Dr. Meyer?

11:26.352 --> 11:27.387
I don't believe so. Heh, heh.

11:27.562 --> 11:29.553
Come.
Tell me what's going on with your son.

11:29.731 --> 11:31.767
LISA: My father was murdered?
RESSLER: Yes.

11:31.983 --> 11:34.690
By people who thought he had sinned.

11:34.861 --> 11:37.944
It might help us find his killer
if we knew that was true or not.

11:38.156 --> 11:40.522
-Was it?
-Yeah.

11:40.742 --> 11:42.698
That's why I ran away.

11:42.911 --> 11:44.822
So can I ask
how you treat the children?

11:44.996 --> 11:46.361
You know, how it all works.

11:47.207 --> 11:49.619
It's important for me
to get a sense of the child...

11:49.792 --> 11:52.625
...so the first few sessions
would be one-on-one.

11:52.837 --> 11:54.543
Without a parent present?

11:54.714 --> 11:58.081
For me to gain their trust,
it's best to start out that way.

11:58.301 --> 12:00.587
lwas 12.

12:00.803 --> 12:03.294
I came home from swimming
at my friend's house...

12:03.473 --> 12:06.055
...went into the basement
to put my suit in the dryer...

12:06.226 --> 12:07.432
...and he was there.

12:07.936 --> 12:09.767
-Your father.
-And someone else.

12:10.104 --> 12:11.435
A boy.

12:11.648 --> 12:14.606
When you're alone with my son,
would you be touching him?

12:14.859 --> 12:16.440
Heh. Absolutely not.

12:16.653 --> 12:18.484
I'm not sure
I understand your question.

12:18.655 --> 12:21.362
I mean,
would you think about touching him?

12:25.036 --> 12:28.528
I'm sorry your son is having a hard time,
but I think you should leave.

12:33.002 --> 12:37.086
-Unh. No. No. What are you doing?
HOLT: You hurt children.

12:37.257 --> 12:39.464
-No.
-You earn their trust then abuse them.

12:41.052 --> 12:43.589
They said I was crazy.

12:43.763 --> 12:47.927
That I was making it all up.
That my father never raped that little boy.

12:48.142 --> 12:49.973
But I know the truth.

12:50.561 --> 12:53.394
My father was a monster.

12:54.440 --> 12:56.772
Whoever killed him
did the world a favor.

12:56.943 --> 13:00.026
-Sooner or later, we all pay for our sins.
-No. What are you doing?

13:00.196 --> 13:01.902
What is this? What are you doing?

13:02.115 --> 13:03.150
I paid for mine...

13:03.324 --> 13:07.033
-What are you talking about?
-...and it's time you pay for yours.

13:12.208 --> 13:14.665
Oh, we meet again.
You must be the new neighbor.

13:14.877 --> 13:16.162
-l'm Zoe.
-Liz.

13:16.379 --> 13:17.368
Who's this?

13:17.588 --> 13:20.204
-Stanley.
-Hi, Stanley.

13:20.383 --> 13:22.874
Ha-ha-ha. Hi, Stanley.

13:23.052 --> 13:24.428
He's so cute.

13:24.637 --> 13:26.719
Don't let that fool you.
He's the devil child.

13:26.931 --> 13:29.138
