by who did.

25:06.547 --> 25:08.378
Red, you know me. You know Brenda.

25:08.590 --> 25:11.582
You think we'd be living in the Bentley
if we didn't have to?

25:11.802 --> 25:14.339
If you're not controlling The Vehm,
then who is?

25:14.513 --> 25:16.253
