27:10.546 --> 27:12.161
RESSLER:
Jared Locke's victim...

27:13.215 --> 27:14.295
...he doesn't exist.

27:14.466 --> 27:17.503
You were given a screen grab of a model
from a children's website.

27:17.678 --> 27:20.135
You killed William Bosker
for molesting his nephew...

27:20.305 --> 27:22.796
...in Akron, Ohio on June 23rd.

27:22.975 --> 27:25.808
