are necessary sacrifices...

30:25.198 --> 30:26.904
...for the good of the holy church.

30:27.117 --> 30:29.278
[LAUGHING]

30:29.453 --> 30:32.445
No sin in murder
or money laundering...

30:32.622 --> 30:35.955
...so long as it serves our father
here on earth...

30:36.126 --> 30:37.161
.uoryou.

30:48.138 --> 30:51.471
Donald Ressler, FBI. I understand
