30:51.641 --> 30:54.257
-I am. Is something wrong?
-I need to see him right now.

30:54.436 --> 30:55.801
-He stepped out.
-Call him.

30:55.979 --> 30:59.062
He has me hold his phone.
Says it messes up the lines in his suit.

30:59.232 --> 31:01.063
l have nothing to confess to you.

31:01.276 --> 31:02.561
Oh, that.

31:02.778 --> 31:04.814
I wasn't really interested in hearing it.

31:04.988 --> 31:09.197
Although I suppose life in the abbey
must be full of intrigue.

31:09.368 --> 31:13.156
What I am interested in
is a proposition.

31:13.330 --> 31:15.241
Care to hear it?

31:15.457 --> 31:16.697
[CLANKING]

31:24.174 --> 31:26.711
[w]

31:36.228 --> 31:37.513
[THUMPING]

31:45.195 --> 31:47.026
RICHARDS:
You have a job for The Vehm?

31:47.239 --> 31:48.228
I do.

31:48.407 --> 31:51.444
One that should appeal to you.
It's a money Iaunderer

31:51.618 --> 31:54.735
A formidable player
who presents a significant obstacle...

31:54.913 --> 31:57.655
...to anyone interested
in clearing the playing field.

31:57.874 --> 31:59.535
-Who is it?
-Contact The Vehm.

31:59.709 --> 32:02.917
Tell them to meet us here.
I'll explain everything then, not before.

32:03.505 --> 32:04.995
-They're busy.
-Hm.

32:05.424 --> 32:09.918
The FBI raided their chamber of horrors.
Killed one, captured some others.

32:10.095 --> 32:14.008
They'll talk,
and when they do, they'll talk about you.

32:14.182 --> 32:17.219
So my proposition is this:

32:17.436 --> 32:19.176
Do what I'm asking, do it now...

32:19.354 --> 32:21.515
...and I'll make sure
you go someplace quiet...

32:21.690 --> 32:23.976
